# Input

```grit

pattern identifier_scope($name) {
  or {
function($parameters) where {
      $parameters <: contains $name
    },
  }
}

```


# Formatted

```grit
pattern identifier_scope($name) {
	or { function($parameters) where { $parameters <: contains $name } }
}

```
